Like any athlete, we draw upon every feedback and focus on improvement for better performances.
Recently we have worked on:

- HR Monitor: you can check your heart rate during your training and save data
- New notification panel: you will receive your customized push notification about the activities done and planned on the My Movement section of the app

Like any athlete, we draw upon every feedback and focus on improvement for better performances.
Recently we have worked on:

- Eye-catching and completely redesigned graphics, which makes the app easier to navigate
- Tab bar with 4 different environments: to FACILITY AREA, MY MOVEMENTS and RESULTS, the SETTINGS environment is now added. There you can leave your feedbacks, sync your apps, connect your heart rate band and learn more about MOVEs and MOVERGY.
- Featured classes: In this new section of FACILITY AREA you will find the most innovative group lessons of your club: let’s try them all!
- Next Classes: In FACILITY AREA you can see which group lessons are scheduled in your club every day, including the ones that are about to start: book your place now!
- Featured programs: in FACILITY AREA you will find the programs prepared for you by the best trainers in your club: start to train now!
- Book the classes of your interest in different clubs: in MY MOVEMENT area you will always have a complete overview of the classes you have booked, regardless of the center where you have decided to do them.
- Bug fix

This time we have introduced one of most asked features:
now you can train with mywellness app and find all your results saved on Apple Health app!

For expedite users we have enabled quick actions:
everyone has a 3D Touch device will complete in a few clicks the most common operations, such as connecting to an equipment or adding a workout result.

Of course there is no shortage of bug fix and small improvement to the user experience.

Your feedback is very important, keep on sending your advices and suggests!

We are always taking into account your feedbacks; this time we have worked to offer you an even better training experience with these latest news ready for you:

- We have developed a new graphic solution for the workout details pages and for the "Results" area
- We have added a new feature on the results graphics: now you can see the comparison between your performance and the one prescribed by your trainer.
- We have introduced the Heart Rate monitor sync: now you can track your bpm in all your trainings simply by connecting your heart band or wereable device with mywellness app. You will check real-time if you're in the recommended heart rate zone.
- We have resolved the display problems on the graphs of the "Results" area which you recently pointed out
- We have solved many bugs, but if you find any more, report them to us!

- Rate your session: evaluate your workout experience to help us improve your next training session
- We have solved many bugs, but if you find any more, report them to us!

We work for you to get the best from your training; this time we have introduced the features you requested most:

Ensuring maximum transparency on the collection and processing of your personal data is very important for mywellness: we have introduced some changes aimed at strengthening the protection of your sensitive data.
The main changes concern your visits to one or more clubs:
- When you select your club or other clubs near you through the "My clubs " feature, you will be asked to consent to the processing of your data by that club
- You can choose to set up your profile as Public or as Private. If you set it as Private, your training data will no longer appear in the club's leaderboards and challanges; your profile picture and your data will no longer be visible to the other users when you book the classes.

These changes, aimed at a greater protection of your rights to privacy, allow us to be compliant with the standards of the new General Data Protection Regulation of the European Union (GDPR).

This time, we have worked to improve the user experience of the class booking feature: you can now book and unbook the classes of your club in an easier and simpler way; you can also receive a reminder to know when to book the classes you would like to join. You can add custom filters to view and book the class activities you are interested in, on the days and hours you prefer, with your favorite trainer.
